headline: Homebuilders rise on rate cut odds, VinFast posts wider Q3 loss
summary: Market Catalysts host Julie Hyman tracks several of the day's top trending stock tickers, including the share gains for homebuilders PulteGroup (PHM), D.R. Horton (DHI), and KB Home (KBH); Elastic (ESTC) stock sliding lower after reporting slowing cloud business growth; and Vietnamese EV manufacturer VinFast Auto (VFS) publishing a wider-than-expected loss for its third quarter. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.
